Mode how the data is handled. Mode=0 means filtering by mean. Mode=1 means filtering with by median. Mode=2 means filtering by median first and then by mean. Mode=10, 11, 12 is equivalent, but parts with invalid areas can be handled. In these areas the rank has to be zero.
